title: Beyonce, Rihanna, others sue Paris firm over clothing knockoffs
text: NEW YORK/PARIS (Reuters) - Beyonce, Jay Z, Kanye West, Pharrell Williams and Rihanna have jointly sued a Paris clothing retailer they say has been "brazenly" selling shirts, hats, backpacks, mobile phone cases and other items featuring their likenesses without permission. Â»
